{
  "text": "To test the effect of various filter parameters and compare the results to ordinary linear isotropic filters, we began our numerical optimization on artificial data. In contrast to Ref. [CITATION_1] , we now are dealing with 2-D substructures in a 3-D domain. We designed four different test geometries \u0351see Table 1 and Fig. 3\u0352 .",
